article.description: — Jahvon Blair had 22 points as Georgetown romped past Coppin State 80-48 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Blair scores 22 to carry Georgetown over Coppin State 80-48
article.linkText: Blair scores 22 to carry Georgetown over Coppin State 80-48
article.story: WASHINGTON -- — Jahvon Blair had 22 points as Georgetown romped past Coppin State 80-48 on Tuesday night. Jamorko Pickett had 19 points and 18 rebounds for Georgetown (2-2). Chudier Bile added 13 points and eight rebounds, and Donald Carey had eight rebounds. Koby Thomas had 12 points and 10 rebounds for the Eagles (0-4). Chereef Knox added 12 points and Anthony Tarke had five steals. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
